  "Name": {
    "English": "ATLAS FIREWORK PACK",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "阿特拉斯烟花包",
    "TraditionalChinese": "寰宇煙火包"
  },
  "NameLower": {
    "English": "Atlas Firework Pack",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "阿特拉斯烟花包",
    "TraditionalChinese": "寰宇煙火包"
  },
  "Subtitle": {
    "English": "Pyrotechnics Multi-Pack",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "烟火技术组合包",
    "TraditionalChinese": "煙火表演組合包"
  },
  "Description": {
    "English": "A three-variety pack of luxury fireworks. These stunning pyrotechnics render the likeness of an Atlas Interface, in bursts of <span class=\"name name-technology\">indium</span>, <span class=\"name name-commodity\">gold</span> and <span class=\"name name-fuel\">cadmium</span>. Ignite to create glittering displays in the sky.<br><br>Place launch tube via the <VAL_ON>Build Menu<> (<span class=\"name name-img\">BUILD_MENU</span>). <span class=\"name name-fuel\">Warning</span>: Aim away from living creatures. Not recommended for indoor use.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一包包含三种奢华烟花的组合包。这些惊人的烟花含有<span class=\"name name-technology\">铟</span>、<span class=\"name name-commodity\">金</span>和<span class=\"name name-fuel\">镉</span>，在空中爆发后，呈现出阿特拉斯表层界面。点燃它，你就可以在天空中开启一场炫丽的光影表演。<br><br>可以通过<VAL_ON>建造菜单<>（<span class=\"name name-img\">BUILD_MENU</span>）来放置发射筒。<span class=\"name name-fuel\">警告</span>：不可瞄准活体生物。不建议在室内使用。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "三種豪華煙火的組合包，令人驚奇的火焰技術，施放時爆發出多道<span class=\"name name-technology\">銦</span>、<span class=\"name name-commodity\">金</span>與<span class=\"name name-fuel\">鎘</span>的光芒。在天空中描繪出寰宇介面的畫像。點燃即可在天空中創造出絢爛效果。<br><br>可從<VAL_ON>建造選單<>（<span class=\"name name-img\">BUILD_MENU</span>）放置發射管。<span class=\"name name-fuel\">警告</span>：請勿對著生物發射，不建議於室內使用。"
  },
